                        <li><span class="code-badge">10-3</span> Retour sur fréquence</li>
                        <li><span class="code-badge">10-4</span> Bien reçu</li>
                        <li><span class="code-badge">10-8</span> Prise de service</li>
                        <li><span class="code-badge">10-10</span> Fin de service</li>
                        <li><span class="code-badge">10-14</span> Escorte / Convoi</li>
                        <li><span class="code-badge">10-20</span> Localisation actuelle</li>
                        <li><span class="code-badge">10-31</span> Coups de feu</li>
                        <li><span class="code-badge">10-32</span> Fusillade</li>
                        <li><span class="code-badge">10-50</span> Accident</li>
                        <li><span class="code-badge">10-55</span> Délit de fuite</li>
                        <li><span class="code-badge">10-60</span> Vente de drogue</li>
                        <li><span class="code-badge">10-61</span> Braquage de Banque</li>
